<P class=MsoNormal 0pt? 0in **Zowie**?MARGIN:><SPAN ?Century Gothic?? 10pt; **Zowie**?FONT-SIZE: FONT-FAMILY:>&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN ?Century Gothic?? 10pt; **Zowie**?FONT-SIZE: FONT-FAMILY:>Currently being discussed  This is almost just like being evaluated however these items the development team is totally undecided if they want to implement or how to do so.&nbsp; The Community Team plans to give updates on these types of items every 2 weeks, even if its just a no change since the last update</SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 0pt? 0in **Zowie**?MARGIN:><SPAN ?Century Gothic?? 10pt; **Zowie**?FONT-SIZE: FONT-FAMILY:>&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN ?Century Gothic?? 10pt; **Zowie**?FONT-SIZE: FONT-FAMILY:>Done  This means that the development team has implemented this item and its currently on live servers.</SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 0pt? 0in **Zowie**?MARGIN:><SPAN ?Century Gothic?? 10pt; **Zowie**?FONT-SIZE: FONT-FAMILY:>&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN ?Century Gothic?? 10pt; **Zowie**?FONT-SIZE: FONT-FAMILY:>Currently on Test server  This means that the development team has implement this item and its currently on test server, watch for future updates for implementation on the live servers.</SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 0pt? 0in **Zowie**?MARGIN:><SPAN ?Century Gothic?? 10pt; **Zowie**?FONT-SIZE: FONT-FAMILY:>&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN 10pt; **Zowie**?FONT-SIZE: FONT-FAMILY: Verdana?>Waiting for community feedback&nbsp; This means we dont have enough information to make any type of decision on how to implement.&nbsp; Threads will be started by me to get your feedback.</SPAN><SPAN ?Century Gothic?? 10pt; **Zowie**?FONT-SIZE: FONT-FAMILY:></SPAN></P>
