<P class=MsoNormal 0in auto? mso-margin-top-alt: mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; 0pt; **Oompa-Loompa**?MARGIN:><SPAN **Oompa-Loompa**?COLOR: #cccccc?><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman">- the aggro/assist radii for harmony should match pacify <FONT color=#0000ff>[possibly in&nbsp;upgrade with omens]</FONT></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 0in auto? mso-margin-top-alt: mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; 0pt; **Oompa-Loompa**?MARGIN:><SPAN **Oompa-Loompa**?COLOR: #cccccc?><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman">- need upgraded harmony with higher level cap <FONT color=#0000ff>[possibly in upgrade with omens]</FONT></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 0in auto? mso-margin-top-alt: mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; 0pt; **Oompa-Loompa**?MARGIN:><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman"><SPAN **Oompa-Loompa**?COLOR: #cccccc?>5.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Snare issues&nbsp; </SPAN><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN red? **Oompa-Loompa**?COLOR:>(currently being evaluated)</SPAN><SPAN **Oompa-Loompa**?COLOR: #cccccc?></SPAN></FONT></FONT></FONT></P>
