<P class=MsoNormal 0in auto? mso-margin-top-alt: mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; 0pt; **Oompa-Loompa**?MARGIN:><SPAN **Oompa-Loompa**?COLOR: #cccccc?><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman">-&nbsp;upgrade to AoE snare with resist modifier and greater speed reduction (so it is not overwritten)</FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 0in auto? mso-margin-top-alt: mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; 0pt; **Oompa-Loompa**?MARGIN:><SPAN **Oompa-Loompa**?COLOR: #cccccc?><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman">- fewer immune mobs</FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 0in auto? mso-margin-top-alt: mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; 0pt; **Oompa-Loompa**?MARGIN:><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman"><SPAN **Oompa-Loompa**?COLOR: #cccccc?>6.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Improved Aggro Management&nbsp; </SPAN><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN **Oompa-Loompa**?COLOR: blue?>(no change planned at this time)</SPAN><SPAN **Oompa-Loompa**?COLOR: #cccccc?></SPAN></FONT></FONT></FONT></P>
