<P class=MsoNormal 0in auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: mso-margin-top-alt: auto? 0pt; **Oompa-Loompa**?MARGIN:><SPAN **Oompa-Loompa**?COLOR: #cccccc?><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman">- druids have single target versions, which are insufficient, particularly&nbsp;in the high end game</FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 0in auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: mso-margin-top-alt: auto? 0pt; **Oompa-Loompa**?MARGIN:><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman"><SPAN **Oompa-Loompa**?COLOR: #cccccc?>10.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Improved run speed&nbsp; </SPAN><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN **Oompa-Loompa**?COLOR: red?>(currently being evaluated) UPDATED BY COMMUNITY</SPAN><SPAN **Oompa-Loompa**?COLOR: #cccccc?></SPAN></FONT></FONT></FONT></P><SPAN **Oompa-Loompa**?COLOR: #cccccc?><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman">
<P><SPAN><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman">-&nbsp;"Spirit of Horse": &nbsp;faster SoW closer to run speed of&nbsp;higher end horse or&nbsp; base Selo's,&nbsp; with or without lev effects (floating effect of FoE causes motion sickness, excessive lag for many players)</FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P><SPAN><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman">-&nbsp;faster SoW;&nbsp;&nbsp;indoor SoW</FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P><SPAN><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman">-&nbsp;revised Spirit of Cheetah spell (druid only, longer duration, no long recast time)</FONT></FONT></SPAN></P></FONT></FONT></SPAN></SPAN></DIV></BLOCKQUOTE>
