<P class=MsoNormal 0pt; auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: mso-margin-top-alt: auto? 0in **Zowie**?MARGIN: justify; TEXT-ALIGN:>Malosinia<BR>Decrease Cold Resist by 70<BR>Decrease Magic Resist by 70<BR>Decrease Poison Resist by 70<BR>Decrease Fire Resist by 70<BR>Resist: Magic no adjust</P>
<P class=MsoNormal 0pt; auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: mso-margin-top-alt: auto? 0in **Zowie**?MARGIN: justify; TEXT-ALIGN:>Malos <BR>Decrease Cold Resist by 55<BR>Decrease Magic Resist by 55<BR>Decrease Poison Resist by 55<BR>Decrease Fire Resist by 55<BR>Resist: Unresistable</P>
